<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Frequently Asked Questions</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/gmblogo.png">
    <style>
        body, html{
            background-image: url('/images/contactbackground.jpg');
            margin: 0;
            height: 100%;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: center;
            background-size: cover;
        }

        .back-button {
            position: absolute; 
            top: 50px; 
            left: 50px;
        }

        .back-button a {
            display: block; 
        }

        .back-button img {
            display: block; 
            width: 50px; 
            height: auto; 
        }

        .faq-container{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            border-radius: 15px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(199, 115, 37, 0.89);
            padding: 20px; 
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin: 0vh auto 10vh;
            max-width: 80%;
            width: 100%; 
            max-height: 70%;
            height: 100%;
            box-sizing:content-box;
            position: relative;
            top: 10%;
        }

        #content {
            height: 700px; 
            overflow-y: auto;
            padding-left: 100px;
            padding-top: 80px;
            width: 100%;
            
            }

        #content > .content-item {
            display: flex;
            max-width: max-content;
            align-items: center;    
            justify-content: flex-start;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 10px;
            padding: 10px;
            width: 90%;
            border-bottom: 1px solid black;
            
            
            }
        
        .content-item h2 {
            text-align: left;
            font-size: large;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            margin-right: 50px;
            color: rgba(199, 115, 37, 0.89);

            }
    
        .content-item p {
            text-align: justify;
            font-size:medium;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: rgba(199, 115, 37, 0.89);
            } 
        
        .content-item h3 {
            text-align: left;
            justify-content: flex-start;
            font-size:medium;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-left: 10px;
            margin-right: 8px;

            }
        .location {
            font-size: medium;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: rgba(199, 115, 37, 0.89);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.5s ease;
            margin-left: 10px;
            margin-right: 8px;
            }

        .location:hover{
            color: black;
            } 

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="faq-container">
        <div class="back-button">
            <a href="/" target="_self">
                <img src="/images/backbutton.png" alt="Back" />
            </a>
        </div>

        <div id="content">

            <div class="content-item">
                <h2>Is there a dog shelter?</h2>
                <h3>Yes, there is. Here is the Facebook link :</h3>
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/gmbbarinak" target="_blank" class="location">Famagusta Municipality Dog Shelter and Rehabilitation Center</a>
            </div>

            <div class="content-item">
                <h2>What are your sister municipalities?</h2>
                <h3>Our sister municipalities are :</h3>
                    <a href="https://www.izmir.bel.tr/" target="_blank" class="location">Ä°zmir Municipality</a>
                    <h3>|</h3>
                    <a href="https://www.antalya.bel.tr/" target="_blank" class="location">Antalya Municipality</a>
                    <h3>|</h3>
                    <a href="https://www.struga.org/" target="_blank" class="location">Struga Municipality</a>
            </div>

            <div class="content-item">
                <h2>What needs to be done to become a new water subscriber? What are the required documents?</h2>
                
                <h3>A document proving that the house, office, or land belongs to you (Title Deed or Sales Agreement) - 
                        Building Permit - Site Plan (Plot Map) - Building Inspection Approval or Permanent Connection Certificate - A photocopy of the ID card of the person who will take the water -  
                       | It is required to apply in person to the Famagusta Municipality with these documents.</h3>
               
            </div>

            <div class="content-item">
                <h2>What are some important phone numbers?</h2>
                <h3>Emergency Health - 112</h3>
                <h3>|</h3>
                <h3>Police Emergency - 155</h3>
                <h3>|</h3>
                <h3>Fire Department - 199</h3>
                <h3>|</h3>
                <h3>Forest Fire - 177</h3>
                <h3>|</h3>
                <h3>Coast Guard - 158</h3>
            </div>

            <div class="content-item">
                <h2>How can I transfer the water subscription of the apartment I rented to the tenant?</h2>
                <h3>Rental Agreement - 
                    Tenant's Identity Card and a photocopy of the ID card - 
                    Receipt of the fee paid to the Municipality Cashier |
                    With these documents, the tenant must apply in person to the Municipality.</h3>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>